room_title: Escape room "Ralph Breaks VR" by The Void Orlando in Orlando
room_address: 1732 East Buena Vista Drive Orlando, FL 32836
room_description:
Join arcade game stars Wreck-It Ralph and Vanellope von Schweetz to sneak into the internet where you and your friends will travel inside the coolest video games. While you’re at it, be sure to survive an epic food fight at the Pancake Milkshake Diner.It's time to break into the internet! Get ready for Ralph Breaks VR, the immersive virtual adventure by ILMxLAB, The VOID, and Walt Disney Animation Studios.

In Ralph Breaks VR, you and up to three friends or family will sneak onto the internet alongside Wreck-It Ralph and Vanellope von Schweetz. Together you’ll play the newest, coolest video game ever and have the ultimate food fight in Pancake Milkshake Diner.
